---
title: Tangy Beef Stir-Fry with Fresh Noodles and Broccoli
description: Although we have a whole slew of different noodles to choose from for our Asian dishes, yakisoba is one of our all-time favorites. A quick stir-fry in the pan is all it takes for them to become tender. With crispy beef, tender broccoli, and aromatics, this dish puts instant ramen to shame.
